  <front>
    <title>Authenticating FMIPv6 Handovers</title>
    <seriesInfo name="Internet-Draft" value="draft-haddad-mipshop-fmipv6-auth-02"/>
    <author initials="W." surname="Haddad" fullname="Wassim Haddad">
      <organization>Ericsson Research</organization>
    </author>
    <author initials="S." surname="Krishnan" fullname="Suresh Krishnan">
      <organization>Ericsson Research</organization>
    </author>
    <date day="26" month="September" year="2006"/>
    <abstract>
      <t>This document specifies a scheme to secure the handover signaling in
   FMIPv6 using one way hash chains.  The values generated in a one way
   hash chain will be used one at a time during each handoff to
   authenticate the signaling messages.</t>
    </abstract>
  </front>
